        {
            "title": "歐洲央行管委Panetta稱必須防止戰爭引發的通膨推高工資",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"歐洲央行\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:歐洲央行;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/歐洲央行\">歐洲央行</a>管理委員會成員Fabio <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Panetta\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Panetta;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Panetta\">Panetta</a>表示，決策者必須防止戰爭引發的通膨推高工資，同時提醒稱政策反應不宜過強。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">義大利央行行長Panetta周二在羅馬出席該行年度股東大會時表示，伊朗危機的影響可能比當前席捲中東的衝突持續更久。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「高度不確定的環境正在形成，並可能延續至劇烈衝突階段之後，」他表示，「必須密切關注預期，防止工資-價格螺旋式上升，同時確保貨幣政策行動保持適度，與歐洲央行的使命相一致。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-78076f64-e272-343f-98a6-ac5009b6288c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Panetta的言論反映出，隨著戰爭進入第二個月，歐洲央行的政策思路可能正在演變。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「與2022年俄羅斯入侵烏克蘭後類似，在高度不確定的情況下，貨幣政策再次面臨負面供給衝擊，」Panetta表示，同時補充道，現在的利率設置已經不同。「與2022年相比，當前貨幣政策在維護價格穩定方面處於更有利的位置。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他引述歐洲央行預測稱，無論事態如何發展，今年通膨都將高於2%的目標，同時經濟成長將更為疲弱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「如果能源衝擊比基準情景更強、更持久，通膨將進一步上升，而經濟成長將更加疲弱，」他補充道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Panetta還談及歐洲央行當前另一項關鍵舉措。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「數字歐元將作為現金的補充，而非替代，旨在為公眾提供一種安全、免費的支付方式，可在任何情況下使用，包括離線環境，」他表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Panetta Says ECB Must Avoid Wage-Price Spiral Spurred by War (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E7%AE%A1%E5%A7%94panetta%E7%A8%B1%E5%BF%85%E9%A0%88%E9%98%B2%E6%AD%A2%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E7%9A%84%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E6%8E%A8%E9%AB%98%E5%B7%A5%E8%B3%87-153031935.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-01 00:27:11",
